No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico.

Motion of the River Master for approval of fees and expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded a total of $2,885.93 for the period April 1 through June 30, 2000, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 530 U. S. 1212.]
